headline: Jaan Health Secures $25M to Transform Care for Millions of Chronically Ill Patients
summary: Jaan Health, the company behind the AI-powered proactive care platform Phamily©, announced it has secured more than $25 million in funding to accelerate the transformation of between visit care for millions of patients struggling with chronic conditions.
